title: NFL Owners Meetings: Matt Nagy, Frank Reich & Adam Gase
itunes:title: NFL Owners Meetings: Matt Nagy, Frank Reich & Adam Gase
description:
A room filled with heroes- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling & Marc Sessler- are live in Orlando, Florida for the annual owners meetings. The heroes sit down with the new Bears head coach Matt Nagy, Colts head coach Frank Reich and Dolphins coach Adam Gase.
